name: Andy & Samy Tee
description:
The official "Andy & Samy Show" T-Shirt!

This tee is inspired by some of Andy & Samy's favorite colors! Pink is for their spunky, fun personalities and black is for their edgy moments!

The kids tee (shown in the image to the left) is printed on a Gymboree kids unisex t-shirt, and the teens & adults are printed on Gap/Jcrew unisex vnecks & will fit just about anyone!

small = medium for girls
medium = large for girls
large= xlarge for girls

All of your purchases are very much appreciated and help in the production and development of "The Andy & Samy Show" and help the girls in their journey to stardom! :] Thank you!
